1. `expo/app/_layout.tsx` — Add SplashScreen control, startup timeout, visible loading/error states
2. `expo/lib/auth-context.tsx` — Add timeout to `initAuth`, ensure `isLoading` always resolves
3. `expo/app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx` — Improve loading state with timeout fallback

